result.name: Yuen Hing Lung Noodles

reviews.text: A place for noodles 🍝 must come.  Owners are friendly and helpful he can speak different languages too. His wife is helping for order and serving cum cashier very busy during lunch and dinner.  The best is in the afternoon and after dinner time   👍👍👍👍👍👍😜😜😜😜😇😇😇

Probably the best traditional HK style noodle I ve ever had! Staff are friendly and helpful, you feel warm And caring when you are there. (They got enough air con though) 
Items you cannot miss:-
Jarjung noodle (dry) - signature
鯪魚球is superb - signature
水餃you couldn’t miss
Beef ball &貢丸 are lovely - not easy to find elsewhere 
Fresh beef slices are awesome
Their noodle are unbeatable - must eat 
瀨粉is definitely another choice if you do not fond of noodle - even you don’t fond of noodle I still recommend you to do here

Was coming here for their famous jajangmein   炸醬麵 fried bean paste noodles.  Their version use thin sliced pork and ketsup.  But it's not meant to be as they were sold out when I came at 3pm.  Was told best time for it is when they open at 11:30am.
So I tried their squid tentacles rice noodles.  Squid was fresh and good $30.

Traditional fish ball noodles with a reasonable price.
Also have some new tweaks.
Great noodles at keen prices

result.name: 源興隆麵家

reviews.text: 麵靚👍

A place for noodles 🍝 must come.  Owners are friendly and helpful he can speak different languages too. His wife is helping for order and serving cum cashier very busy during lunch and dinner.  The best is in the afternoon and after dinner time   👍👍👍👍👍👍😜😜😜😜😇😇😇

這間有60多年開業嘅麵店虽然店舖細細。但其出品都勝過很多麵家。𠵱咖已經轉由第二代人打理。但仍然保持住上一代開創者嘅水準！湯底十分够水準！配合埋爽口嘅生麵係一種絕妙嘅享受。有出色嘅傳統雲吞，牛腩及牛筋，亦有好食嘅特色炆香菇等任君選擇。有出名嘅薑葱撈麵和炸醬撈麵。每樣出品都正！！各位朋友如果有興趣想去試下保証唔會失望。地點係西環皇后大道西近山道之傍。101及104等過海巴士可到達。地鐵係香港大學山道出口。
地方太少、常滿座、有鄉土味 ;招呼太好！
香港嘅舊風味麵家食物口味同質量中上'
